{"title":"幸福生活来到了","authors":["沈彭年"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":9,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福生活来到了（快板）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沈彭年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党中央，毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大旗一指拿主意。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个主意无价宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五亿农民都说好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无价宝，宝无价，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"名子就叫公社化。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农业社、小并大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从今以后天不怕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕涝，不怕旱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"玉皇龙王随手转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五谷丰登吃不了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一亩小麦打十万。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕穷，不怕白，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两大革命一齐来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"技术、文化闹革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闹得地动天也动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农村干起大工厂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进村好像进了城。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又是农，又是工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又做买卖又当兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"办了中学办大学，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农民又是大学生。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人都是多面手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八臂哪吒难夸口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"组织起来军事化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行动起来战斗化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过日子，集体化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三化好处非常大。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社化成一巨人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"移山倒海不嫌沉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能倒海，能搬山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拳头一举碰着天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党中央，毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大旗一指拿主意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个主意无价宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农民欢呼公社好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社好，公社好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福生活来到了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（附图片）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（人民美术出版社供稿）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}